<br>
EP-loot (molds and patterns only):<br>
<br>
Type    Members  Drops <br>
Chain    18 (20%) 49 (23%) <br>
Leather 16 (18%) 41 (19%) <br>
Plate     30 (34%) 69 (32%) <br>
Silk       25 (28%) 54 (25%) <br>
Total    89 (100%) 213 (100%) <br>
<br>
As you can see (if the formatting dont suck) is that we have been VERY lucky. 34% of our guild is plate class and 32% of molds have been plate. But then we could use more clerics ... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub147.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ormethesingingbard>Orme the Singing Bard</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://66.192.193.136/images/homer.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Minstrel</span><br>  Posts: 291<br> <font color=#330000>(2/8/04 12:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=18895.topic&index=12>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Elemtal armor drop %</span><hr size=1> Just think how much better it would be if bards were a leather class.  That would just make so much more sense.  You'd have less leather rot and less plate demand.  Oh well.  No point. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub147.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nanan>Nanan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Minstrel</span><br>  Posts: 217<br> <font color=#330000>(2/8/04 7:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=18895.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Elemtal armor drop %</span><hr size=1> They should of just had a symbol of the armor slot as the drop, the symbol being universal among the armor types. This would reduce the rot issue 