<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>You just beat Rallos Zek ... now what?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Kill RZ again, and again, and again....Did I mention to kill him again?<br>
You are far from done farming RZ for your warriors, it's a necessary evil.<br>
<br>
Pulling:<br>
I still don't know...our guild is wrapped in the holy trinity of only monks can pull mentality and they are not ready to give up their position, so I just kick back and let them do their thing.<br>
<br>
Equipment:<br>
Hope you have points saved up. I personally save most of my points for the rarest of drops....elem armor will eventually trickle your way so there's no point in jumping out of the gate and spending your raid points on it.<br>
You've gone without it this long and if the tribal mask,corns spaulders, mephit talon, Etc...drops you'll want to be able to outbid the other melee classes who will certainly be bidding with you.<br>
<br>
Thats just my opinion of course...some grab elem armor asap..but it will still be dropping when your guild has &quot;transcended&quot;  the mobs that drop the the items mentioned above.<br>
<br>
Solo:<br>
Fire has a couple of spots but most prefer the &quot;tables&quot; camp for soloing...it's a 14%exp per 8-10 min chant kite...and boring as hell.<br>
Your better off with a group...personally I exp in hard advents these days but I remember poe being awesome exp...or even pow if you can convince people into going. You may get lucky and get a named to drop bard swarm weapon.<br>
<br>
In general bard drops are pretty rare, and the ones that do seem to drop (non instrument) are also desired by other<br>
classes.<br>
Example: I had to max bid on a mephit talon against a rogue who rightfully would have loved the 12% BS mod.<br>
<br>
Gratz on elementals but I'm sorry to inform you to bust out the overalls and mount your combine...It's time to farm!<br>
<br>
Jordell Da' Maestro <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=18895.topic&start=21&stop=24>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showPrevMessage?topicID=18895.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showNextMessage?topicID=18895.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=18895.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.emailToFriend?topicID=18895.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.threadControl?topicID=18895.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=18895.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=18895.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valig